    {
      "text": "Tom and Jerry: The Movie (トム＆ジェリー ザ ムービー), also known as Tom and Jerry, is a platform game developed by SIMS and published by Sega in 1992 for the Master System. In 1993, the game was converted to the Game Gear with completely different stages, but the same gameplay. The game was released to coincide with the film of the same name, but has no relevance to the film's content.",
